Krusen Capital,aabhas@myasiavc.com,"Krusen Capital Management (KCM) is an investment advisor based in New York, New York. Founded in 2009, the firm provides investment solutions for family offices, high net worth individuals, and select independent wealth advisers. Additionally, the firm focuses on identifying actionable investment themes, conducting due diligence, recommending managers and investment opportunities, and re-balancing portfolios over time Our goal is to capture a targeted risk-adjusted return and specifically, alpha. Krusen Capital's advisory platform currently provides investment solutions in hedge funds, private equity funds, credit funds, real estate, and venture capital funds. The financial sophistication of the client base provides important insights and feedback to the whole ecosystem.","United States, New York United States, New York New York United States, Americas, North America, Great Lakes, New York Metro",Research,[],,Family Offices,[],0,,,,"[""Seed Round"", ""Early stage VC"", ""Later stage VC"", ""Buyout""]","AI and Machine Learning, Finance, Robotics",,,,http://www.linkedin.com/company/krusen-capital-management,https://www.krusencapital.com,,,,Charles Krusen,charles.krusen@krusencapital.com,12128230809,CIO,http://www.linkedin.com/in/charles-krusen-471235,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
