Kevin Mitchell,aabhas@myasiavc.com,"Redcloud Capital invests equity capital in lower middle-market companies with revenues between $20 million and $100 million, with minimum operating profits of $3.5M. The firm focuses on buy-and-build consolidations in fragmented industries and growth capital investments where additional funding is required to execute an expansion strategy. Redcloud pursues investments in a wide range of industries with an emphasis on high value-added services and niche manufacturing. Typical equity investments range between $10 million and $40 million per transaction.","United States, Colorado United States, Denver Colorado United States, Americas, North America, Mountain",Research,[],,Angel Investors / HNW,[],0,,,,"[""Seed Round""]","Professional Services, Industrial Technology, Deep Tech",,,,https://www.redcloudcap.com/,,,,,Kevin Mitchell,kjm@redcloudcap.com,"","",,,https://www.redcloudcap.com/,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
