Houston Exponential,aabhas@myasiavc.com,"Houston Exponential is a Fund of Funds with the primary goal of achieving a compelling return for investors while also attracting venture capital firms to bring their expertise and risk capital to the region. It was created to accelerate the development of Houston's innovation economy by fostering a robust ecosystem that supports high-growth, high-impact startups. The firm invests in companies operating in the Industrial IoT, robotic, advanced material, healthcare, manufacturing, cybersecurity and artificial intelligence sectors.","United States, Texas United States, Houston Texas United States, Americas, North America",Research,[],,Fund of Funds,[],0,,,,"[""Seed Round"", ""Early stage VC"", ""Later stage VC""]","Cybersecurity, Manufacturing, Health & Wellness (LOHAS), AI and Machine Learning, IoT, Robotics",Texas,,,https://www.houstonexponential.org/,,,,,Guillermo Borda,gborda@hxventurefund.com,"",Managing Partner,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
